# SchoolClubs — Full Technical Documentation

## 1. Overview

SchoolClubs is a web application for managing school clubs built with **ASP.NET Core 8.0 MVC**. It allows students to browse clubs, join them, attend events, earn achievements, and compete on a leaderboard. Teachers and administrators can create/manage clubs, events, announcements, and view analytics.

The application features a bilingual interface (Bulgarian / English), a dark/light theme toggle, role-based access control via ASP.NET Core Identity, and automatic database seeding — making it fully portable across machines with no migrations required.

