## 11. Services

### AchievementService
- `CheckAndAwardAchievements(userId)` — Evaluates all achievements against user's activity and awards unearned badges
- `CheckCriteria(userId, achievement)` — Checks specific criteria: clubs joined, events attended, days as member, announcements made, photos uploaded
- `GetTotalPoints(userId)` — Sums all points from user's earned achievements
- `GetLeaderboard(count)` — Returns top N users by points with rank
- `GetUserRank(userId)` — Returns the user's position in the leaderboard

### ClubRecommendationService
- `GetRecommendations(userId, count)` — Returns recommended clubs based on user's category preferences; falls back to popular clubs for new users

