## 15. Security

- **Authentication:** ASP.NET Core Identity with cookie-based authentication
- **Authorization:** Role-based (`[Authorize(Roles = "Admin")]`) and claim-based checks
- **Anti-forgery:** All POST forms include `@Html.AntiForgeryToken()` and controllers validate with `[ValidateAntiForgeryToken]`
- **Password policy:** Min 6 chars, requires uppercase, lowercase, and digit; no non-alphanumeric required
- **Input validation:** Data annotation attributes on all view models with server-side validation
- **File upload security:** File type and size validation on gallery photo uploads (max 5MB)
- **SQL injection prevention:** Entity Framework parameterized queries throughout
- **XSS prevention:** Razor auto-encoding of all output
